==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Peddling
<hw>Ped"dling</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Hawking; acting as a
peddler.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Petty; insignificant; trifling; paltry; piddling; --
now less common than <altname>piddling</altname>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
miserable remains of a <xex>peddling</xex> commerce.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> petty; insignificant; trifling; paltry;
piddling.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pederast</ent>⟦br⟧
